The paper discusses the physical design of mission/safety-critical circuits and systems, which falls under the category of Embedded Systems (cs.ET). The paper also discusses fault tolerance and redundancy schemes, which are relevant to the categories of Architecture (cs.AR), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Electromagnetics (cs.EM), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
